L&	 zùù	&	type of weather	\\	
HL&	lɔ́ʊ̀	& 	hartebeest	\\
LH&	 bìé	&  	child		\\
\end{Qtabular}
}
\qquad
\subfloat[][Two light syllables CVCV]{
\begin{Qtabular}{llp{3cm}}
  
